50 CartesianPath::CartesianPath() {
51  auto& p = properties();
52  p.declare<double>("step_size", 0.01, "step size between consecutive waypoints");
53  p.declare<double>("jump_threshold", 1.5, "acceptable fraction of mean joint motion per step");
54  p.declare<double>("min_fraction", 1.0, "fraction of motion required for success");
55 }

59 bool CartesianPath::plan(const planning_scene::PlanningSceneConstPtr& from,
60  const planning_scene::PlanningSceneConstPtr& to, const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg,
61  double timeout, robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectoryPtr& result,
62  const moveit_msgs::Constraints& path_constraints) {
63  const moveit::core::LinkModel* link = jmg->getOnlyOneEndEffectorTip();
64  if (!link) {
65  ROS_WARN_STREAM("no unique tip for joint model group: " << jmg->getName());
66  return false;
67  }
68 
69  // reach pose of forward kinematics
70  return plan(from, *link, to->getCurrentState().getGlobalLinkTransform(link), jmg, timeout, result, path_constraints);
71 }

73 bool CartesianPath::plan(const planning_scene::PlanningSceneConstPtr& from, const moveit::core::LinkModel& link,
74  const Eigen::Isometry3d& target, const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg, double timeout,
75  robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectoryPtr& result,
76  const moveit_msgs::Constraints& path_constraints) {
77  const auto& props = properties();
78  planning_scene::PlanningScenePtr sandbox_scene = from->diff();
79 
80  kinematic_constraints::KinematicConstraintSet kcs(sandbox_scene->getRobotModel());
81  kcs.add(path_constraints, sandbox_scene->getTransforms());
82 
83  auto is_valid = [&sandbox_scene, &kcs](moveit::core::RobotState* state, const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg,
84  const double* joint_positions) {
85  state->setJointGroupPositions(jmg, joint_positions);
86  state->update();
87  return !sandbox_scene->isStateColliding(const_cast<const robot_state::RobotState&>(*state), jmg->getName()) &&
88  kcs.decide(*state).satisfied;
89  };
90 
91  std::vector<moveit::core::RobotStatePtr> trajectory;
92 #if MOVEIT_MASTER
93  double achieved_fraction = moveit::core::CartesianInterpolator::computeCartesianPath(
94  &(sandbox_scene->getCurrentStateNonConst()), jmg, trajectory, &link, target, true,
95  moveit::core::MaxEEFStep(props.get<double>("step_size")),
96  moveit::core::JumpThreshold(props.get<double>("jump_threshold")), is_valid);
97 #else
98  double achieved_fraction = sandbox_scene->getCurrentStateNonConst().computeCartesianPath(
99  jmg, trajectory, &link, target, true, props.get<double>("step_size"), props.get<double>("jump_threshold"),
100  is_valid);
101 #endif
102 
103  if (!trajectory.empty()) {
104  result.reset(new robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory(sandbox_scene->getRobotModel(), jmg));
105  for (const auto& waypoint : trajectory)
106  result->addSuffixWayPoint(waypoint, 0.0);
107 
108  trajectory_processing::IterativeParabolicTimeParameterization timing;
109  timing.computeTimeStamps(*result, props.get<double>("max_velocity_scaling_factor"),
110  props.get<double>("max_acceleration_scaling_factor"));
111  }
112 
113  return achieved_fraction >= props.get<double>("min_fraction");
114 }
